dc_title_s: Bass River State Forest brochure front
dc_creator_sm: New Jersey. Dept. of Conservation and Economic Development
dc_description_s: Front of brochure published by the New Jersey Department of Conservation and Economic Development on Bass River State Forest. Front includes a table of campsites available and descriptions of the bathing facilities, cabin and boat rentals and hunting grounds. There is also a paragraph on Lake Absegami, now called Absecon.
